imdb.title: Tokko
imdb.plot: When 108 demons free themselves and start killing people, Special Public Safety Task Force, or "Tokko" for short, is formed to stop them. Some of the members have demons inside of them and can use them to enhance their own abilities.

episodes.title: Awakening
episodes.plot: It's only Ranmaru's first day on the police beat, but zombies from another dimension don't seem to care. After a close call, Ranmaru meets the elite police unit that specializes in zombie ass-kicking: Tokko. Japan is (once again) under attack by evil demons, ghoulish zombies, and the devil himself. Gumshoe agent Ranmaru Shindo joins the elite Tokko team to slice through the bad guys and avenge the death of his parents. Tokko is filled with twists and turns and will keep you guessing about the true nature of evil until the very end.
